<span id="pagelocation"><span class="pagepath"><a href="/community/SwitchingToUbuntu">SwitchingToUbuntu</a><span class="sep">/</span><a href="/community/SwitchingToUbuntu/FromWindows">FromWindows</a></span><span class="sep">/</span><a href="/community/SwitchingToUbuntu/FromWindows/Configuring">Configuring</a></span>
